Lost the picture myself Brian, I know that area very well, did some walleye fishing in the area myself, and a lot of bass fishing! Looking at some of the pictures? It has sure changed in 14 or so years!
Both members of the first place team won a ranger 620 and split a check for 25k, not a bad weekend of fishing?  107 and change for 15 fish.
Better then the K Lakes where you look for 4 of the fattest 50cm fish you can find, for many years we use to cull those, now they are the ones you need to win
